text: Admetula marshalli is a species of sea snail, a marine gastropod mollusc in the family Cancellariidae, the nutmeg snails. ==References== * Bouchet P. & Petit R.E. (2008). New species and new records of southwest Pacific Cancellariidae. The Nautilus 122(1): 1-18 Category:Cancellariidae Category:Gastropods described in 2008
title: Admetula marshalli
